.TH "snd_hda_get_connections" 9 "snd_hda_get_connections" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hda_get_connections \- copy connection list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hda_get_connections
.BI "(struct hda_codec *codec "  ","
.BI "hda_nid_t nid "  ","
.BI "hda_nid_t *conn_list "  ","
.BI "int max_conns "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "codec" 12
the HDA codec
.IP "nid" 12
NID to parse
.IP "conn_list" 12
connection list array; when NULL, checks only the size
.IP "max_conns" 12
max. number of connections to store
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Parses the connection list of the given widget and stores the list
of NIDs.

Returns the number of connections, or a negative error code.
